title: Australian student loans extended to long-term residents from NZ (Department of Education and Training - ...
text: ( Source : Department of Education and Training - Australian Government ) New Zealand citizens who have been long-term residents of Australia since childhood will be given access to the Australian student loans programme from 1 January 2016 .
